=====Usage notes=====
Although an adverb, {{m|nl||heel}} may be inflected as well ({{m|nl|hele}}) to match the following adjective, by analogy with the inflection of adjectives in Dutch.

. For example, both of these sentences are correct:
* {{ux|nl|Dat is een '''heel''' grote boom.|That is a '''very''' large tree.}}
* {{ux|nl|Dat is een '''hele''' grote boom.|That is a '''very''' large tree.}}
The latter form may be regarded as informal and less appropriate for formal writing.

